{"id":"entities/simplebaby","title":"SimpleBaby","type":"entities","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. SimpleBaby is the working product name Yahir gave his <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/baby-tracking-app\">baby tracking app</a> prototype — \"a secure baby tracker that's easy to use\" with Sleep / Feeding / Nursing / Diaper / Milestone / Health log categories. First mentioned in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-6-50-56-pm-fe7f3d85\">2025 03 16 screenshot 2025 03 16 at 6 50 56 pm fe7f3d85</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","related":[{"id":"projects/baby-tracking-app","label":"Privacy-Friendly Baby Tracking App (CS 461 capstone)"},{"id":"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-7-01-47-pm-c70df294","label":"SimpleBaby — first-child onboarding"},{"id":"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-7-03-48-pm-fceecb78","label":"SimpleBaby — Logs/Trackers tab layout"},{"id":"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-6-50-56-pm-fe7f3d85","label":"SimpleBaby — welcome / sign-in screen"}]}
